<font size=2><table width="100%" bgcolor="#004b97"><font color=#d2d200><b>Borik's Box</b></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=1><a style="color: #ffffff" href="mailto:jcsmith@amazinghideaways.com?subject=Regarding: Borik's Box">Submit Info</a></font></table>
<font color=white><br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Classes:</b></font> Any<br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Recommended Level</b>:</font> 55<br><b><font color=#d2d200>Quest Rating:</b></font> 

Good


<br>
<br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Starting NPC:</b></font> <a style="color:#ffffff" href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Borik%20Darkanvil%22">Borik Darkanvil</a><br>

<b><font color=#d2d200>Starting Zone:</font></b> Plane of Knowledge<br>

<b><font color=#d2d200>Related Zones:</font></b> Plane of Innovation, Plane of Nightmare, Plane of Valor<br>



<br><b>Related Quests:</b><br><a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqquestfull&eqquests.quest_name=%22Halls%20of%20Honor%20Entrance%22">Halls of Honor Entrance</a>
<br>



<br><b>Related NPCs:</b><br><a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22A%20Corroded%20Prototype%22">A Corroded Prototype</a><br>


<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Agony%20Mephit%22">Agony Mephit</a><br>


<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Grenic%20Drere%22">Grenic Drere</a><br>


<br><b>Reward(s)</b>:<br>

<font color=#d2d200>Box of Souls</font><br>

<br>
<font color=#d2d200><b>Description:</b></font><br>
This quest is given by Borik Darkanvil in the Plane of Knowledge. He can craft you a box that you can then use in a quest beginning with Grenic Drere in the Plane of Valor(see related quests). This information was obtained from a <a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/feqtraderscornerfrm77.showMessage?topicID=141.topic">EQ Traders Thread</a>.<BR><BR>You say, 'What box of souls?'<BR><BR>Borik Darkanvil says, 'Bork Anvil's eyes grow narrow' So your looking to capture some souls are you? its non of my Business I suppose so dont answer. I'm pretty sure that I dont want to know. I paid heavily for the formula for the Box of souls, but its not a price I would pass on to anyone else. There isnt much to it, but it does take the hands of a skilled smith and the magic of Tanaan's forges to even attempt it. For you will need a Block of [Perilium].<BR><BR>You say, 'What Block of Perilium'<BR><BR>Borik Darkanvil says, Perilium was once used to make clockwork machines, there are now stronger metals so it has become harder and harder to find Perilium, much less a block that is large enough to be of any use. Then you will need to find the brain of a crystal spider, this is where the actual will be held. Of course the box will need a supernatural power source, the souls are held into place by the horror of there own dreams, the heart of an agony mephit will give the device power. Forge these with a smithing hammer and a vial of sacred water and you will have your box. Of course if you have not the skill, I can [forge them for you].<BR><BR>You say, 'I wish you to forge them for me.'<BR><BR>Borik Dark Anvil says, if you return all 3 items to me I will do the work for you, a mere 3 thousand platinum. I will not guarantee my success, but I can guarantee if you do not have the skill, you will fail.'<BR><BR><font color=#dddd00>The block of Perilium drops on Corroded Prototypes in the Plane of Innovation.<BR><BR>Agony Mephit Hearts drop on Agony Mephits in the Plane of Nightmare.<BR><BR>Crystal Spider Brains drop on Luminii Crawlers in the Plane of Valor.<BR><BR>Once you have these three items there are two ways to obtain the Box of Souls. The first is to hand those three items to Borik Darkanvil along with 3000pp and he will craft the box for you.<BR><BR>The second way is to combine those three items + a Vial of Sacred Water(drops in the Sergeants in the Plane of Valor) + a Smithy Hammer in a Forge. I would only recommend this if you are a very skilled Smith.<BR><BR>Once you obtain a Box of Souls you can use it for the Halls of Honor Entrance quest originating with Grenic Drere in the Plane of Valor(see related quests).</font><br><br>
<br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Submitted By:</font></b> Heartsong Steelsoul<br><br>


